  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate whether high frequency airflow oscillation (HFAO), delivered using Aerosure,
      increases six minute walk distance (6MWD) and reduces exertional breathlessness in patients
      with severe chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
